<html>

	<head>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"/>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
		<style>
			#email-body {
				color: #5d1e4e;
				font-family: sans-serif;
				background-color: #fff !important;
			}

			#email-root {
				margin: auto;
				max-width: 600px;
				background-color: #fef9f7;
				padding: 16px;
			}

			#email-header {
				margin: auto;
				max-width: 600px;
				padding: 16px;
				text-align: center;
				color: #5d1e4e;
			}

			#email-footer {
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				max-width: 600px;
				text-align: center;
				padding: 16px;
				padding-top: 0px;
				margin: auto;
				margin-top: 24px;
			}

			.bold-green {
				font-weight: bold;
				color: #eb7334;
			}

			.light-green-background {
				background-color: #fef9f7; 
			}

			#email-group {
				text-align: center;
				margin-top: 24px;
			}

			.button {
				border: 0;
				cursor: pointer;
				display: inline-flex;
				outline: 0;
				position: relative;
				align-items: center;
				user-select: none;
				vertical-align: middle;
				justify-content: center;
				text-decoration: none;
				-webkit-appearance: none;
				-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
				padding: 6px 16px;
				font-size: 0.875rem;
				min-width: 64px;
				box-sizing: border-box;
				transition: background-color 250ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 0ms, box-shadow 250ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 0ms, border 250ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 0ms;
				font-weight: 500;
				line-height: 1.75;
				border-radius: 4px;
				letter-spacing: 0.02857em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				box-shadow: 0px 3px 1px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0px 2px 2px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14), 0px 1px 5px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
				color: #fff;
				background-color: #eb7334;
				margin: 8px;
			}
			.button .button-label {
				cursor: pointer;
				user-select: none;
				-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
				font-size: 0.875rem;
				font-weight: 500;
				line-height: 1.75;
				letter-spacing: 0.02857em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #fff;
				box-sizing: inherit;
				width: 100%;
				display: inherit;
				align-items: inherit;
				justify-content: inherit;
			}
			.button .button-start-icon {
				cursor: pointer;
				user-select: none;
				-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
				font-size: 0.875rem;
				font-weight: 500;
				line-height: 1.75;
				letter-spacing: 0.02857em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #fff;
				box-sizing: inherit;
				display: inherit;
				margin-left: -4px;
				margin-right: 8px;
			}
			.button .button-start-icon .button-icon-root {
				cursor: pointer;
				-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
				font-weight: 500;
				line-height: 1.75;
				letter-spacing: 0.02857em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #fff;
				box-sizing: inherit;
				fill: currentColor;
				width: 1em;
				height: 1em;
				display: inline-block;
				transition: fill 200ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 0ms;
				flex-shrink: 0;
				user-select: none;
				font-size: 20px;
			}
		</style>
		<title>::theme.name::</title>
	</head>

	<body id="email-body">
		<div id="email-header">
			<b>::group.name::</b>
		</div>
		<div id="email-root">
			::raw __content__::
			<div id="email-group">
				<a class="button" href="http://::HOST::/group/::group.id::" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener notrack">
					<span class="button-label">
						::group.name::
					</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div id="email-footer">
			<img src="http://::HOST::/theme/::theme.id::/logo3.png" alt="logo ::theme.name::" style="margin-bottom: 16px; max-width: 200px; max-height: 87px;"/>
			<p>Ce courriel a été envoyé depuis <a href="http://::HOST::" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener notrack">::theme.name::</a>.</p>
			<p>Vous recevez ce message car vous faites partie de <b>::group.name::</b>::if list!=null:: (::list::) ::end::</p>
			::if (user!=null)::
			<p><a href="::user.getEditNotificationsLink(group)::" rel="notrack">Changer les préférences de notification</a></p>
			<p><a href="::user.getQuitGroupLink(group)::" rel="notrack">Quitter ce groupe</a></p>
			::else::
			<p>Pour ne plus recevoir de message, veuillez <a href="https://wiki.amap44.org/fr/app/Utilisation-de-CAMAP#quitter-un-groupe" rel="notrack">quitter ce groupe</a>
			::end::
		</div>
	</body>

</html>